  "description": "One day in the peaceful village of Puru in the world of Fillip Side, Mui and Popuri were playing in the forest. They happened upon a strange shrine, and suddenly from the sky came a young girl. Her name is Madoka, but other than that, she doesn't remember anything about who she is or where she's from. Not knowing what else to do, she decides to stay with Mui and his family, helping out with errands around the village...<br><br><i>Purumui Purumui</i> is a self-described &quot;morphing RPG&quot;, an action RPG which includes elements of <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=A+Boy+and+His+Blob\">A Boy and His Blob</a> and cooking games like <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?game=Cooking+Mama\">Cooking Mama</a>. Madoka can find or purchase different ingredients, then use them to prepare different dishes, which when fed to Mui result in different transformations including bridges and ladders, as well as different types of weapons for use in the dungeons.",
